OL,3,CTeenage boy stabbed to death as
OL,4,Cmachete fight breaks out after party
OL,6,FA teenage boy has been stabbed to
OL,7,Fdeath after a fight spilled out of a
OL,8,Fhouse party in Hackney, police said.
OL,10,FOfficers were called after a large
OL,11,Fgroup of people with machetes were
OL,12,Fseen on Towpath Walk shortly after
OL,13,F7.15pm on Monday, with some callers
OL,14,Fsuggesting they had also heard
OL,15,Fgunshots.
OL,17,FThe boy was found with stab wounds in
OL,18,Fnearby Poplar Close, but despite the
OL,19,Fefforts of medics from both the land
OL,20,Fand air ambulance, he was pronounced
OL,21,Fdead at the scene.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
