OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779887471
OL,3,CTeenage boy stabbed to death as
OL,4,Cmachete fight breaks out after party
OL,6,FDetectives are working to formally
OL,7,Fidentify the victim, who the Met said
OL,8,Fwas a teenager but did not give an
OL,9,Fexact age, and tell his family.
OL,11,FDetective Chief Inspector Ben Massink
OL,12,Fsaid: "Our thoughts remain with the
OL,13,Fvictim and his family ` we are working
OL,14,Fat pace to ensure all his loved ones
OL,15,Fare informed and offered specialist
OL,16,Fsupport from officers.
OL,26,@tD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
