CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779887471
OL,3,CTeenage boy stabbed to death as
OL,4,Cmachete fight breaks out after party
OL,6,F"For members of the local community,
OL,7,Fwho will no doubt be shocked and
OL,8,Fsaddened by the events of yesterday
OL,9,Fevening, increased police patrols are
OL,10,Fin place in the area. If you have any
OL,11,Fquestions or concerns, do not hesitate
OL,12,Fto speak with one of our officers.
OL,14,F"Urgent enquiries continue to
OL,15,Festablish exactly what happened. We
OL,16,Fknow there were a significant number
OL,17,Fof people in the area at the time of
OL,18,Fthe stabbing, and some individuals
OL,19,Frecorded the incident on their mobile
OL,20,Fphone.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
