CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1779887471
OL,3,CTeenage boy stabbed to death as
OL,4,Cmachete fight breaks out after party
OL,6,F"I would urge anyone who witnessed
OL,7,Fwhat happened or who has footage of
OL,8,Fthe incident to come forward to police
OL,9,F` your information could be vital. I
OL,10,Fwould also ask those with videos or
OL,11,Fphotographs not to post this on social
OL,12,Fmedia out of respect for the bereaved
OL,13,Ffamily."
OL,15,FAnyone with information can call
OL,16,Fpolice on 101, quoting the reference
OL,17,FCAD 6692/25May, or to remain anonymous
OL,18,Fcontact Crimestoppers on 0800 555 111
OL,19,For online.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@HO]
